{
  "stem": "25834.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And sometimes the young fellow was killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And many people was, this time, killed. 200,000 people was almost destroyed in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was one of the biggest, you know, battle, civilian battle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can say so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what happened-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] end of the 30 days, we supposed to surrender.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some part of people with the guns go through the canal to the other part of the town and fight again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We was-- I was very close to my family, the house, and was without ammunition.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I meet my parents and daughters-- sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was maybe six hour after I meet my family, the German go to a basement and ask everybody out-- [GERMAN] And we go to buy food to outskirt the Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Later, to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was like depot of the-- depot of the trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A big car.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was selection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Old people on one side, young people on the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, young, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because young was fighting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother and father go on one side-- supposed to go on one side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my parents would not separate from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Meantime, they a couple hours before, I prepare some agreement with the German who was an Austrian fellow who was working for-- for the physician who selected the people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I give her each person from my family-- $20, gold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what happened-- we supposed to, after a couple hours, go away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, not go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the meantime, a Red Cross from Switzerland arrived to the camp, and SS not like show the people there, so many.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Throw us, everybody to the car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this agreement-- what I make, with this German-- Austrian guy, disappear.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
